# Empty static-output directory.
#
# Vercel's build pipeline expects an "outputDirectory" of static assets
# (default "public/") even for serverless-function-only projects.
# Without it, deploys fail with:
#   Error: No Output Directory named "public" found after the Build completed.
#
# Every request is rewritten to /api/index per vercel.json#rewrites, so
# nothing in this directory is ever served. The .gitkeep exists only to
# create the directory in git.
